# Web App Environment Configuration

## API Configuration
VITE_API_URL=/api/v1
VITE_SOCKET_URL=
VITE_DEV_API_PROXY=http://localhost:3001

## Authentication
VITE_JWT_KEY=axiom_auth_token

## Map Configuration (Mapbox or Google Maps)
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk_live_your_mapbox_token
